The amplification pulse was held at SG-3 Bermuda until September 11, 2001. On September 11, the ''Dove '' group (Jehovian Annunaki), using the Phoenix wormhole at A7/L4, and the ''White Eagle'' group (Necromiton-Andromie Alpha-Omega), using the Falcon wormhole, simultaneously transmitted two massive sub-space ''Trumpet Pulses.'' The Trumpet Pulses were projected from the Falcon/Phoenix wormholes through Ley Line-3 to the Bermuda Base. At the Bermuda Base, the Trumpet Pulses were then combined into one, accelerated via the stored amplification pulse and directed from the Bermuda Base through the Montauk-Phi-Ex Port Interface Network and into the subterranean WTC NYC Phoenix Spike location.
